Detailed Description

cvmx_bgx::_cmr::_rx_stat0

These registers provide a count of received packets that meet the following conditions: * are not recognized as PAUSE packets. * are not dropped due DMAC filtering. * are not dropped due FIFO full status. * do not have any other OPCODE (FCS, Length, etc).
